Name: Dodge This!
About the game: Build your super cute character and put him in-front of a barrage of bombs, spikes and whatever else can kill you. Dodge this is an awesome and crazy game where you need to stay alive as long as possible. The game gets more difficult the longer you live and only the best reflexes will reach the top. The game is played with the mouse and has a great physics engine to keep everything feeling like you are really getting pounded and blown up!
